Vacation is a 2015 American comedy film written and directed by Jonathan Goldstein and John Francis Daley -LRB- in their directorial debuts -RRB- .
It stars Ed Helms , Christina Applegate , Skyler Gisondo , Steele Stebbins , Leslie Mann , Chris Hemsworth , Beverly D'Angelo , and Chevy Chase .
It is the fifth installment of the Vacation film series serving as both a modernized reboot and a sequel to the original four films .
It is also the second not to carry the National Lampoon name after Vegas Vacation , and was released by New Line Cinema and Warner Bros. on July 29 , 2015 .
the film has received negative reviews from critics but it was a box office success , earning $ 104.9 million on a $ 31 million budget .